# I think right now that Mini has to have at least three atoms per residue,
# hence the virtual atoms.
NAME ZN
IO_STRING  ZN Z
TYPE LIGAND
AA UNK
ATOM ZN   Zn2p  X    2.00
ATOM  V1  VIRT  X    0.00
ATOM  V2  VIRT  X    0.00
ATOM  V3  VIRT  X    0.00
